(8, '1TB Western Digital Harddisk', '1tb-western-digital-harddisk', 6000.00, 'products/nXL0Iq8gjSNj6bENOqVX1q0Qhw4eZ7YCeu9zCfQm.png', NULL, 'Excepteur dolorum na', NULL, NULL, 1, '2025-12-19 23:31:42', '2025-12-21 13:23:16', '2025-12-21 13:23:16'),
(9, 'Mikrotik RB260GSP', 'mikrotik-rb260gsp', 7000.00, 'products/w9QKLhLOO8kipsKVPuLyYN86HeRb3m0lCksJIfuQ.png', 'The Mikrotik RB260GSP is a small SOHO switch, which features power output on its ethernet ports. Ports 2-5 can power other PoE capable devices with the same voltage as applied to the unit (passive PoE over datalines only). The RB260GSP has five Gigabit Ethernet ports and one SFP cage, switching is done by an Atheros Switch Chip. The device is running an operating system designed specifically for MikroTik Switch products  SwOS.\n\nCheck out the list of Routers', '<h1>MikroTik RB260GSP: Compact 6-Port Gigabit PoE Switch with SFP</h1>\nThe MikroTik RB260GSP is a compact 6-port Gigabit Ethernet switch designed specifically for small networks that require both high-speed connectivity and power distribution over a single cable. This versatile switch combines five copper Gigabit ports with one SFP fiber optic port, making it ideal for connecting a variety of devices while offering flexible uplink options.\n<br><br>\n<h1>Power Over Ethernet Capability</h1>\nThe switch provides passive PoE (Power over Ethernet) output on ports 2-5, allowing you to power compatible devices like wireless access points, IP cameras, and other network equipment directly through their Ethernet cables. The passive PoE delivers the same input voltage supplied to the switch itself (commonly 12-57V DC depending on your power adapter), simplifying power management for compatible MikroTik and third-party devices.\n<br><br>\n<h1>Advanced Networking Features</h1>\nOperating on MikroTik\'s dedicated SwitchOS (SwOS), the RB260GSP offers enterprise-level management capabilities through an intuitive web interface. You can configure VLANs for network segmentation, monitor traffic statistics, set up port isolation, and manage MAC filteringall without command-line complexity. The Atheros switch chip ensures reliable, wire-speed performance with minimal latency for all connected devices.\n<br><br>\n<h1>Dual Connectivity Options</h1>\nWith five 10/100/1000 Mbps Ethernet ports for local device connections and one SFP cage for fiber optic or copper uplinks, this switch provides flexible deployment options. The SFP port enables long-distance connections up to several kilometers when used with appropriate fiber modules, making it suitable for connecting separate buildings or extending network reach beyond copper limitations.\n<br><br>\n<h1>Professional Applications</h1>\nIdeal for SOHO environments, retail locations, small offices, or as an edge switch in larger installations, the RB260GSP delivers professional switching capabilities in a rugged, metal housing. Its compact design allows for desktop placement or wall mounting, while the passive PoE functionality reduces cable clutter and simplifies installations for powered network devices.\n<br>\n<br>\nPerfect for powering MikroTik wireless access points, connecting surveillance cameras, creating small office networks, or establishing fiber uplinks to main network infrastructureall in one cost-effective, energy-efficient package.', NULL, 'mikrotik', 11, '2025-12-21 12:33:44', '2025-12-21 12:37:57', NULL),
(10, 'Mikrotik SXT SQ 5AC RBSXTSQG-5ACD', 'mikrotik-sxt-sq-5ac-rbsxtsqg-5acd', 7000.00, 'products/jgBOLypvIBmThtxBNjxXNEXOGrxzuKqXedq21WUb.png', 'MikroTik SXT Sq 5 ac (RBSXTSQG-5ACD): High-Performance Dual-Chain Sector Antenna with Gigabit Connectivity\n<h2>High-Gain Dual-Chain Sector Antenna</h2> <p>The device features an <strong>integrated 18 dBi dual-polarization (MIMO) sector antenna</strong> with a 60-degree horizontal beamwidth, providing excellent coverage and signal stability for client connections. The dual-chain design supports full 2x2 MIMO, effectively doubling data throughput and improving link reliability in challenging wireless environments.</p>', 'MikroTik SXT Sq 5 ac (RBSXTSQG-5ACD): High-Performance Dual-Chain Sector Antenna with Gigabit Connectivity\n<h2>High-Gain Dual-Chain Sector Antenna</h2> <p>The device features an <strong>integrated 18 dBi dual-polarization (MIMO) sector antenna</strong> with a 60-degree horizontal beamwidth, providing excellent coverage and signal stability for client connections. The dual-chain design supports full 2x2 MIMO, effectively doubling data throughput and improving link reliability in challenging wireless environments.</p><h2>Powerful Wireless Performance</h2> <p>Equipped with a <strong>QCA9984 chipset</strong>, the SXT Sq 5 ac delivers impressive wireless performance with support for <strong>802.11ac (Wave 2) Wi-Fi standards</strong>, including MU-MIMO technology. It operates in the 5 GHz frequency band with 20/40/80 MHz channel widths, achieving real-world throughput of up to 800+ Mbps, making it suitable for backhaul links or high-density client access.</p><h2>Durability and Environmental Protection</h2> <p>Built for outdoor installation, the device features a <strong>sealed, UV-resistant plastic housing</strong> rated at IP54, protecting it from dust and splashing water. Its compact square shape reduces wind load, and the included versatile mounting bracket allows easy attachment to poles, walls, or towers with adjustable tilt and alignment.</p><h2>Advanced Networking and Power Options</h2> <p>The SXT Sq 5 ac offers <strong>dual Ethernet ports</strong>: one Gigabit port for data and a second port that supports <strong>24V passive PoE output</strong>, allowing you to daisy-chain or power another device such as a camera or another access point. It supports advanced features like Nstreme and NV2 protocols for improved throughput and TDMA-based scheduling for enhanced multi-client performance.</p><h2>Complete with Integrated Cabling</h2> <p>The device comes with <strong>two pre-attached, shielded Ethernet cables</strong> (1.2m and 10m), simplifying installation and ensuring optimal performance in electrically noisy environments. An integrated cable gland provides strain relief and additional weatherproofing.</p><h2>Management and Software</h2> <p>Running <strong>RouterOS Level 4</strong>, the SXT Sq 5 ac provides extensive configuration options through WinBox, WebFig, or the CLI. It supports features such as CAPsMAN central management, multiple SSIDs, VLANs, firewall filtering, and bandwidth management, enabling flexible deployment in both simple and complex network scenarios.</p><p>Ideal for wireless ISPs delivering customer connections, campus or warehouse Wi-Fi coverage, surveillance system backhauls, and enterprise bridging where reliable, high-capacity wireless links are required. Its combination of sector antenna performance, modern 802.11ac technology, and rugged design makes it a cost-effective and efficient solution for professional outdoor wireless networking.</p>\n', NULL, NULL, 11, '2025-12-21 13:24:53', '2025-12-21 13:24:53', NULL),
(11, 'Mikrotik Basebox 5 RB912UAG-5HPnD-OUT', 'mikrotik-basebox-5-rb912uag-5hpnd-out', 8500.00, 'products/8UdUdmkKpToOkmOKWzLewOXm0t2JUTVBJc1WgSxa.jpg', '<h2>High-Power Outdoor Wireless AP/Router</h2> <p>A robust outdoor wireless access point and router with integrated 28 dBi high-gain antenna and IP65-rated weatherproof housing. Designed for establishing long-distance 5GHz wireless links in challenging outdoor environments, ideal for WISPs and remote connectivity.</p>', '<h2>Robust Outdoor Wireless Platform</h2> <p>The MikroTik BaseBox 5 is a high-power, versatile outdoor wireless access point and router built for professional deployments in challenging environments. Housed in a sturdy, die-cast aluminum enclosure with IP65-rated weatherproofing, it is designed to withstand extreme temperatures, moisture, and physical stress, making it ideal for outdoor installations on poles, towers, or building exteriors.</p><h2>High-Power 5 GHz Wireless with 28 dBi Antenna</h2> <p>This unit features an integrated high-gain 28 dBi dual-polarization (MIMO) antenna, providing exceptional signal range and penetration for long-distance links. Operating exclusively in the 5 GHz frequency band, it utilizes a powerful 1 W (30 dBm) transmitter to establish reliable point-to-point or point-to-multipoint connections over several kilometers, even in areas with significant interference or obstacles.</p><h2>All-in-One Networking Device</h2> <p>More than just an access point, the BaseBox 5 functions as a full-featured router running MikroTik\'s RouterOS. It is equipped with a fast 680 MHz MIPS CPU, 128 MB of RAM, and comprehensive networking capabilities including advanced routing, firewall, bandwidth management, and VPN support (PPTP, L2TP, SSTP, OpenVPN).</p><h2>Flexible Connectivity and Power Options</h2> <p>The device includes a Gigabit Ethernet port for the primary network connection and a second 10/100 Mbps Ethernet port with 24V passive PoE output, enabling you to daisy-chain or power another network device like a surveillance camera. It supports a wide input voltage range of 10-30V DC, accommodating various power sources, including solar power systems.</p><h2>Integrated Installation Hardware</h2> <p>For simplified deployment, the BaseBox 5 comes with a complete set of mounting hardware. This includes a robust, adjustable metal mounting bracket (pole/wall mount) and two pre-attached, shielded Ethernet cables of different lengths (1.2m and 10m) that are routed through integrated, sealed cable glands to maintain the IP65 rating.</p><h2>Advanced Management and Software Features</h2> <p>Running RouterOS with a Level 4 license, it offers deep configurability for network professionals. Manage it via WinBox, WebFig, or CLI, and utilize features like CAPsMAN for centralized wireless management, Nstreme and NV2 proprietary protocols for optimized throughput, dynamic frequency selection (DFS), and VLAN support for complex network segmentation.</p><p>Ideal for Wireless ISPs (WISPs) providing last-mile connectivity, establishing long-distance building-to-building bridges, creating outdoor campus Wi-Fi hotspots, or serving as a ruggedized network node in industrial and remote locations. The BaseBox 5 combines high-power radio performance with router-grade functionality in a single, durable outdoor package.</p>', NULL, NULL, 11, '2025-12-21 13:30:14', '2025-12-21 13:30:14', NULL),
(12, 'Mikrotik hAP Lite TC RB941-2nD-TC', 'mikrotik-hap-lite-tc-rb941-2nd-tc', 3000.00, 'products/4KiWnDKmaG89BYqAGOf8NDSlojfeWGuYO7CPYlzY.png', '<h2>Compact Travel Router with Cloud Management</h2> <p>An ultra-portable wireless travel router with cloud management capability, perfect for creating secure networks on the go. Features four Fast Ethernet ports, 2.4 GHz Wi-Fi, and runs on standard USB power.</p>', '\nMikroTik hAP Lite TC (RB941-2nD-TC): Compact Wireless Travel Router with Cloud Management\n<h2>Ultra-Compact Travel and Home Router</h2> <p>The MikroTik hAP Lite TC is a palm-sized, ultra-portable wireless router designed for travelers, students, and home users who need reliable networking in a minimal footprint. Measuring just 113 x 89 mm, this lightweight device can easily fit in a laptop bag or backpack, making it perfect for creating secure wireless networks in hotels, conference rooms, or temporary locations.</p><h2>Dual-Band Wireless Connectivity</h2> <p>This router provides 2.4 GHz wireless connectivity with 2x2 MIMO technology, offering improved range and stability compared to single-chain devices. While operating on the 2.4 GHz band, it supports data rates up to 300 Mbps, sufficient for web browsing, email, and standard-definition video streaming in compact environments.</p><h2>Cloud Management Enabled</h2> <p>The \"TC\" in the model name stands for \"TikCloud,\" indicating built-in support for MikroTik\'s cloud management system. This allows for remote configuration and monitoring without complex networking setupssimply register the device to your MikroTik account and manage it through the cloud portal from anywhere with internet access.</p><h2>Complete Routing Capabilities</h2> <p>Despite its compact size, the hAP Lite TC runs the full-featured RouterOS, providing firewall protection, bandwidth management, hotspot gateway functionality, and VPN support. It features four Fast Ethernet (100 Mbps) ports, allowing connection of multiple wired devices alongside the wireless network.</p><h2>Simple Power Options</h2> <p>The device operates on standard 5V micro-USB power, compatible with most phone chargers, power banks, or USB ports on computers and televisions. This makes it exceptionally versatile for travel use where conventional power adapters might not be available.</p><h2>User-Friendly Operation</h2> <p>With support for multiple operation modesincluding router, access point, bridge, or stationthe hAP Lite TC adapts to various networking needs. The intuitive setup wizard and mobile app compatibility ensure quick configuration even for users with limited networking experience.</p><p>Ideal for travelers needing secure Wi-Fi in hotels, students in dormitories, small home offices requiring basic routing, or as a compact backup networking device. Its combination of cloud management, full RouterOS features, and extreme portability makes it a uniquely versatile solution for mobile networking needs.</p>', NULL, NULL, 11, '2025-12-21 13:33:55', '2025-12-21 13:33:55', NULL),
(13, 'Tp-Link TL-WR840N 300Mbps Wireless Router', 'tp-link-tl-wr840n-300mbps-wireless-router', 1500.00, 'products/KxNZbaD8WgMElBaYzG8LpqPe67bHoI9CiymcxdjZ.webp', 'TP-Link TL-WR840N 300Mbps Wireless N Router\n\n<h2>Reliable Wireless Connectivity for Everyday Use</h2>\n<p>A budget-friendly 300Mbps wireless N router designed to provide stable Wi-Fi coverage for home internet use. With its simple setup, four LAN ports, and essential features like guest network and parental controls, it\'s an accessible solution for basic home networking needs.</p>', 'TP-Link TL-WR840N 300Mbps Wireless N Router\n\n<h2>Reliable Wireless Connectivity for Everyday Use</h2>\n<p>The TP-Link TL-WR840N is an entry-level wireless N router designed to deliver stable and consistent Wi-Fi coverage for everyday home and small office use. Operating on the 2.4 GHz band, it supports wireless speeds of up to 300 Mbps, making it suitable for essential online activities such as web browsing, email communication, social media, and standard-definition video streaming across multiple devices.</p>\n<br><br>\n<h2>User-Friendly Setup and Operation</h2>\n<p>Featuring an intuitive web-based interface and support for the TP-Link Tether app, this router can be configured in minutes without technical expertise. A quick setup wizard guides users through the installation process, while the mobile app allows for convenient network management from a smartphone, including guest network setup and device monitoring.</p>\n<br><br>\n<h2>Versatile Wired Connectivity</h2>\n<p>In addition to its wireless capabilities, the router is equipped with four 10/100 Mbps Fast Ethernet LAN ports for connecting wired devices such as desktop computers, smart TVs, gaming consoles, or network printers. It also includes one 10/100 Mbps WAN port for connecting to your modem or upstream internet source, ensuring a flexible setup for various home network configurations.</p>\n<br><br>\n<h2>Enhanced Network Security Features</h2>\n<p>Built-in security protocols including WPA/WPA2 wireless encryption, an SPI firewall, and IP/MAC/URL filtering help protect your network from unauthorized access and common online threats. Parental controls allow administrators to manage internet access schedules for specific devices, making it easier to supervise childrens online activities.</p>\n<br><br>\n<h2>Guest Network and Bandwidth Control</h2>\n<p>The TL-WR840N includes a dedicated guest network feature, enabling visitors to connect to the internet without accessing your primary local network or shared resources. Integrated bandwidth control allows for basic Quality of Service (QoS) management, helping prioritize traffic for smoother performance during video calls or online gaming.</p>\n<br><br>\n<h2>Compact and Efficient Design</h2>\n<p>Housed in a compact, white plastic enclosure with external antennas, the router is designed to blend into most home or office environments. Its energy-efficient operation minimizes power consumption, and the wall-mount capability helps save space on desks or shelves.</p>\n<br><br>\n<p>Ideal for apartments, student dormitories, small offices, or as a secondary router extending an existing network. With its balance of essential features, straightforward management, and reliable performance, the TL-WR840N offers an accessible and cost-effective networking solution for users with basic connectivity requirements.</p>', NULL, NULL, 21, '2025-12-21 13:38:39', '2025-12-21 13:40:54', NULL),
(14, 'Tp-Link TL-WA801ND', 'tp-link-tl-wa801nd', 2500.00, 'products/TiqU4G1q2QobFpZULbzSpY9fiFtET4Psj7R6jWgn.jpg', '<h2>Versatile Wireless Access Point for Network Expansion</h2><br><br> <p>A flexible 300Mbps wireless N access point designed to extend Wi-Fi coverage in home and office environments. With multiple operating modes and robust connectivity, it provides a reliable solution for eliminating dead zones and adding wireless capability to wired networks.</p>', '<h2>Flexible Wireless Networking Solution</h2> <p>The TP-Link TL-WA801ND is a versatile 300Mbps Wireless N access point designed to extend and enhance wireless connectivity in various environments. Operating on the 2.4GHz frequency band with data rates up to 300Mbps, it serves as a dedicated wireless solution that can transform wired networks into wireless ones or expand the coverage of existing Wi-Fi networks.</p>\n<br><h2>Multiple Operation Modes</h2> <br><p>This device supports several operational modes to accommodate different networking needs, including Access Point mode for creating a wireless network from a wired connection, Repeater mode for extending the range of an existing Wi-Fi signal, Client mode for connecting wired devices to a wireless network, and Multi-SSID for creating up to four separate wireless networks with distinct security settings.</p><br><h2>Robust Hardware Design</h2> <br><p>Featuring two detachable 5dBi antennas with MIMO technology, the TL-WA801ND provides improved signal strength, coverage, and stability compared to single-antenna solutions. The device includes one 10/100Mbps Ethernet port for network connectivity and supports Power over Ethernet (802.3af), allowing for flexible installation locations without requiring proximity to power outlets.</p><br><h2>Enhanced Network Management</h2> <br><p>With comprehensive management features including WPA/WPA2 wireless security encryption, MAC address filtering, and wireless scheduling, the access point offers solid network protection and control. The built-in bandwidth management allows administrators to allocate specific bandwidth to connected devices, ensuring optimal performance for critical applications.</p><br><h2>Professional-Grade Features</h2><br> <p>Supporting advanced functionalities such as WDS bridging for connecting multiple access points without cables, AP Client Router mode for creating a separate subnet, and multiple SSID support for network segmentation, this device offers capabilities typically found in more expensive enterprise-grade equipment while maintaining user-friendly operation.</p><br><h2>Easy Installation and Management</h2><br> <p>The TL-WA801ND can be easily configured through a web-based interface with multiple language support. Its compact design includes wall-mount and ceiling-mount options with a 180-degree adjustable antenna, making installation flexible for various environments from offices and hotels to warehouses and outdoor covered areas.</p><br><p>Ideal for businesses requiring wireless coverage in meeting rooms, hotels offering guest Wi-Fi, educational institutions extending network access, or homes needing to eliminate wireless dead zones. The TL-WA801ND delivers reliable, configurable wireless connectivity that bridges the gap between consumer and professional networking solutions.</p>', NULL, NULL, 21, '2025-12-21 13:47:46', '2025-12-21 13:47:46', NULL),
(15, 'Tenda CP3 Pro 2K Security Camera', 'tenda-cp3-pro-2k-security-camera', 2500.00, 'products/DssZv7MtJfUAFlft4eEcjkv835hJsZsiLAsjxiYr.webp', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Tenda CP3 Pro 2K Security Camera</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Crystal-Clear 2K Monitoring for Home Security</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A wireless indoor security camera delivering 2K QHD resolution, comprehensive motion tracking, and seamless smart home integration. Designed for clear, intelligent monitoring with easy setup and cloud/local storage options.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">Tenda CP3 Pro 2K Security Camera</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">High-Definition 2K QHD Video Quality</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The Tenda CP3 Pro features a high-resolution 2K QHD (2560 x 1440 pixels) image sensor that delivers video quality 1.5 times clearer than standard 1080p Full HD cameras. With enhanced low-light sensitivity and advanced imaging algorithms, it captures sharp, detailed footage day and night, ensuring clear visibility of faces, license plates, and other important details for effective home security monitoring.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Intelligent Motion Tracking and Alerts</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Equipped with advanced AI-powered motion detection, the camera can distinguish between human movement, pets, and general motion. When activity is detected, it automatically follows the subject with smooth 355 horizontal and 100 vertical pan/tilt rotation, keeping the target in the frame while sending instant push notifications to your smartphone through the Tenda Home app.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Versatile Storage Options</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The CP3 Pro offers flexible recording solutions with support for both cloud storage (subscription-based) and local storage via a microSD card (up to 128GB). Continuous recording, motion-triggered recording, and scheduled recording modes provide comprehensive coverage options to suit different security needs and preferences.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Two-Way Audio Communication</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Built-in microphone and speaker enable clear two-way audio communication, allowing you to listen to what\'s happening in real-time and speak through the camera using your smartphone. This feature is ideal for checking in on family members, deterring intruders, or communicating with pets while you\'re away from home.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Smart Home Integration and Privacy Protection</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Compatible with Amazon Alexa and Google Assistant for voice control, the camera can be integrated into existing smart home ecosystems. For privacy, it includes a physical lens cover that can be closed when monitoring isn\'t needed, and all video streams are protected with bank-level 128-bit AES encryption during transmission and storage.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Easy Installation and Setup</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Designed for straightforward DIY installation, the camera connects via 2.4GHz Wi-Fi (802.11n) and requires only a power source. The magnetic base allows flexible placement on any metal surface, while the included mounting bracket enables installation on walls or ceilings. The intuitive Tenda Home app guides users through setup and provides access to all features from anywhere with internet connectivity.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Ideal for monitoring homes, apartments, offices, retail spaces, or childcare facilities, the Tenda CP3 Pro combines high-resolution imaging, intelligent tracking, and user-friendly operation in an affordable package that delivers professional-grade security monitoring for everyday users.</p> </div>', NULL, NULL, 45, '2025-12-21 13:57:36', '2025-12-21 13:57:36', NULL),
(16, 'Dahua DH-HAC-B1A21P 2MP Bullet Camera', 'dahua-dh-hac-b1a21p-2mp-bullet-camera', 2000.00, 'products/eyZrccLKNpIU2eoM0WHOiJvY1qbIuKypT6KHqMNm.jpg', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Dahua DH-HAC-B1A21P</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Professional 2MP Outdoor Bullet Camera with IR Night Vision</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A durable 2MP outdoor bullet camera featuring IR night vision up to 30 meters, IP67 weatherproof rating, and 2.8mm fixed lens. Designed for reliable 24/7 surveillance in residential and commercial security applications.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">Dahua DH-HAC-B1A21P 2MP Bullet Camera</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">High-Quality 2MP Video Imaging</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The DH-HAC-B1A21P features a 2-megapixel progressive scan CMOS sensor that delivers 1080p Full HD resolution at 19201080 pixels. With advanced imaging technology including 3D digital noise reduction (DNR), wide dynamic range (WDR), and true day/night functionality via an IR-cut filter, it captures clear, detailed footage in various lighting conditions with accurate color reproduction during daylight hours.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Powerful IR Night Vision Capability</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Equipped with integrated infrared LEDs, this camera provides effective night vision coverage up to 30 meters (98 feet) in complete darkness. The smart IR technology automatically adjusts LED intensity to prevent overexposure of close objects, ensuring balanced illumination across the surveillance area while maintaining clear visibility of critical details after dark.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Rugged Outdoor Construction</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Built with an IP67-rated weatherproof and dustproof housing, the camera withstands harsh environmental conditions including rain, snow, dust, and temperature extremes from -30C to 60C (-22F to 140F). The vandal-resistant metal casing and robust mounting bracket provide physical protection against tampering and environmental stresses for long-term outdoor deployment.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Wide-Angle Fixed Lens Coverage</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring a fixed 2.8mm lens with a horizontal field of view of 102, the camera offers broad area coverage ideal for monitoring driveways, parking lots, building perimeters, and other open spaces. The fixed focus design ensures consistent image quality without requiring adjustment, simplifying installation and maintenance.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Professional Security Features</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Supporting essential surveillance functionalities including motion detection, privacy masking, and dual video streams (main and sub-stream), the camera integrates seamlessly with Dahua and third-party recording systems. It supports H.264 and H.265 video compression for efficient bandwidth utilization and storage optimization without compromising image quality.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Easy Installation and Integration</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Designed for straightforward installation, the camera includes a versatile mounting bracket with adjustable positioning (0-75 tilt) and cable management system. It supports Power over Ethernet (PoE, 802.3af) for single-cable installation, as well as traditional 12V DC power input, offering flexible deployment options for both new and existing security systems.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Ideal for residential property surveillance, commercial perimeter security, retail parking monitoring, and industrial facility protection. The Dahua DH-HAC-B1A21P combines professional-grade video quality, robust construction, and reliable performance in a cost-effective package suitable for various outdoor security applications.</p> </div>', NULL, NULL, 45, '2025-12-21 14:03:04', '2025-12-21 14:03:04', NULL),
(17, 'DAHUA NVR5464-EI 64 CHANNEL', 'dahua-nvr5464-ei-64-channel', 70000.00, 'products/eRCFTkBKyL75bZMYWlQWnWazz7hoggmOtiaCqEcx.jpg', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">DAHUA NVR5464-EI</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Enterprise 64-Channel 4K NVR with AI Analytics</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A high-performance 64-channel network video recorder supporting 4K resolution, AI-powered video analytics, and dual operating systems. Designed for large-scale surveillance deployments with enterprise-grade reliability and advanced smart features.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">DAHUA NVR5464-EI 64-Channel Network Video Recorder</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Massive 64-Channel Recording Capacity</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The NVR5464-EI supports up to 64 IP camera channels with concurrent recording, playback, and live view capabilities. It handles up to 800 Mbps incoming bandwidth and 768 Mbps outgoing bandwidth, enabling seamless management of large-scale surveillance systems across enterprise campuses, critical infrastructure, and city-wide security deployments.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">4K Ultra HD Resolution Support</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">With advanced video processing capabilities, this NVR supports recording at 12MP/4K resolution across all channels simultaneously. It features H.265+/H.265/H.264+/H.264 video compression technologies, reducing storage requirements by up to 90% compared to traditional H.264 while maintaining exceptional image quality for forensic analysis and evidentiary purposes.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Dual Operating System Architecture</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring Dahua\'s innovative dual OS design, the NVR operates on both Linux and embedded Android systems. This unique architecture allows for simultaneous running of traditional surveillance functions on Linux while supporting third-party applications, AI analytics, and smart features on the Android platform without compromising system stability or performance.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">AI-Powered Video Analytics</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Integrated with advanced artificial intelligence capabilities, the NVR5464-EI supports deep learning algorithms for accurate people counting, facial recognition, vehicle detection, license plate recognition, and abnormal behavior analysis. The AI functions operate at the edge, reducing network bandwidth usage and enabling intelligent search and instant alerting based on specific criteria.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Enterprise Storage and RAID Protection</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Equipped with 8 SATA III interfaces supporting up to 16TB drives each, the system offers massive storage capacity up to 128TB. It supports multiple RAID configurations (RAID 0, 1, 5, 6, 10, 50) for data redundancy and protection against drive failures, ensuring continuous recording integrity for mission-critical surveillance applications.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Advanced Networking and Integration</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The NVR features dual Gigabit Ethernet ports with failover, load balancing, and multi-address modes for network redundancy. It supports ONVIF, PSIA, and CGI protocols for third-party camera integration, as well as comprehensive video management through Dahua\'s DSS Express, DMSS, and SmartPSS software platforms for centralized control of distributed systems.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Professional Surveillance Features</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Including intelligent video retrieval with metadata search, perimeter protection with virtual tripwires, heat mapping for crowd analysis, and multi-level user management with granular permissions. The system supports HDMI and VGA outputs with up to 4K display resolution, 16-channel synchronous playback, and video wall management for control room environments.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Designed for large enterprise security systems, government facilities, transportation hubs, educational campuses, and city surveillance projects. The DAHUA NVR5464-EI delivers enterprise-grade reliability, massive scalability, and intelligent analytics in a comprehensive video management solution for the most demanding surveillance requirements.</p> </div>', NULL, NULL, 49, '2025-12-21 14:07:33', '2025-12-21 14:07:33', NULL),
(18, 'DAHUA DH-HAC-HDW1500TP-IL-A Dome Camera', 'dahua-dh-hac-hdw1500tp-il-a-dome-camera', 3500.00, 'products/Nrj6hoYCxw1gkdy9lOG9O54BcAiM1vP2rrNzh9zB.png', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">DAHUA DH-HAC-HDW1500TP-IL-A</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">5MP IR Dome Camera with Audio</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A high-resolution 5MP vandal-resistant dome camera featuring built-in microphone, 30m IR night vision, and IP67 weatherproof rating. Ideal for indoor and outdoor surveillance requiring clear audio and video evidence capture.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">DAHUA DH-HAC-HDW1500TP-IL-A 5MP Dome Camera</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">5MP High-Resolution Imaging</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring a 5-megapixel CMOS sensor, this dome camera delivers exceptional 25601920 resolution video, providing 2.5 times more detail than standard 1080p cameras. With advanced 3D digital noise reduction (DNR) and true wide dynamic range (WDR) up to 120dB, it captures crisp, clear footage even in challenging high-contrast lighting conditions, making it ideal for identifying faces, license plates, and other critical details.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Built-In Audio Capability</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Equipped with an integrated microphone, the camera enables simultaneous audio and video recording, providing valuable contextual information for security incidents. The built-in audio support allows for two-way communication when connected to compatible systems, enhancing monitoring capabilities for retail environments, entry points, and facilities requiring audio verification alongside visual evidence.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Enhanced IR Night Vision</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">With powerful infrared LEDs providing illumination up to 30 meters (98 feet), the camera delivers reliable 24/7 surveillance capability. The smart IR technology automatically adjusts LED intensity based on scene illumination, preventing overexposure of nearby objects while maintaining optimal visibility of distant targets in complete darkness.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Vandal-Resistant IP67 Design</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The camera features a robust IK10 vandal-resistant dome housing with IP67 environmental protection, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor installations. The impact-resistant construction withstands physical tampering attempts, while the weatherproof sealing protects against dust, rain, and extreme temperatures from -30C to 60C (-22F to 140F).</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Flexible Installation Options</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Supporting multiple mounting configurations including ceiling, wall, and pendant installations, the camera includes an adjustable mounting bracket with 360 rotation capability. It offers dual power options with support for 12V DC power input and features a 3-axis mechanical adjustment mechanism for precise positioning during installation.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Advanced Video Intelligence</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The camera supports essential video analytics including motion detection, tamper alarm, and privacy masking for sensitive areas. Compatible with Dahua\'s Smart H.265+ compression technology, it reduces bandwidth and storage requirements by up to 90% compared to standard H.264, making it cost-effective for large-scale deployments and long-term recording scenarios.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Wide-Angle Coverage</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring a fixed 2.8mm lens with a 108 horizontal field of view, the camera provides comprehensive area coverage suitable for monitoring retail spaces, offices, hallways, and residential properties. The wide-angle perspective minimizes blind spots while maintaining image clarity across the entire surveillance area.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Ideal for retail stores, office buildings, educational institutions, hospitality venues, and residential properties requiring high-resolution surveillance with audio recording capabilities. The DAHUA DH-HAC-HDW1500TP-IL-A combines exceptional image quality, robust construction, and versatile functionality in a reliable dome camera solution for demanding security applications.</p> </div>', NULL, NULL, 45, '2025-12-21 14:11:22', '2025-12-21 14:11:22', NULL),
(19, 'DAHUA DH-ASA-1222E 2MP PTZ Security Camera', 'dahua-dh-asa-1222e-2mp-ptz-security-camera', 13000.00, 'products/qZ3M7gvMky53wjvN44cDPknzt9RPkFOolTaTbgxu.png', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">DAHUA DH-ASA-1222E</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">2MP High-Speed PTZ Dome Camera</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A professional 2MP high-speed PTZ dome camera featuring 22x optical zoom, 360 continuous rotation, and smart tracking. Designed for wide-area surveillance in large facilities, parking lots, and perimeter security applications.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">DAHUA DH-ASA-1222E 2MP PTZ Security Camera</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">22x Optical Zoom Capability</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring a powerful 22x optical zoom lens (f=4.7mm~103.4mm), this PTZ camera provides exceptional long-range surveillance with detailed close-up views of distant subjects. The auto-focus mechanism ensures sharp imaging throughout the zoom range, allowing operators to monitor large areas while maintaining the ability to zoom in on specific incidents or individuals up to several hundred meters away.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">High-Speed Pan/Tilt Movement</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The camera delivers rapid positioning with pan speed up to 300 per second and tilt speed up to 200 per second, enabling quick response to security events across wide surveillance areas. With 360 continuous horizontal rotation and -15 to 90 vertical tilt range, it provides complete hemispherical coverage without blind spots when properly installed.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Advanced Auto-Tracking Technology</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Equipped with intelligent auto-tracking functionality, the camera can automatically detect and follow moving objects within its field of view. The tracking algorithm distinguishes between humans and vehicles, maintaining consistent framing while the subject moves through the surveillance area, significantly enhancing monitoring efficiency for security personnel.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Starlight Night Vision Performance</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring Dahua\'s Starlight technology with a high-sensitivity 1/2.8\" CMOS sensor, the camera delivers exceptional low-light performance with color video in environments as dark as 0.005 lux. Integrated IR LEDs provide illumination up to 150 meters for complete darkness situations, while the IR-cut filter with auto-switch ensures optimal day/night image quality.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">IP66 Weatherproof Housing</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Housed in a robust IP66-rated environmental enclosure, the camera withstands harsh weather conditions including heavy rain, snow, dust, and salt fog. Designed for outdoor operation across temperatures from -40C to 60C (-40F to 140F), it includes a built-in heater and defogger for reliable performance in extreme climates.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Multiple Preset and Patrol Functions</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Supporting up to 256 preset positions, the camera can be programmed to monitor specific areas of interest with one-touch recall. Four pattern patrol routes and eight auto-scan paths enable automated surveillance coverage, while the privacy masking feature allows operators to block sensitive areas from view or recording.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Professional Integration Features</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Compatible with major video management systems through ONVIF, PSIA, and CGI protocols, the camera offers flexible integration options. It supports H.265+/H.265/H.264 video compression, dual-stream encoding, and includes alarm I/O interfaces for connecting external sensors and devices to trigger automated PTZ responses.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Ideal for monitoring large parking facilities, transportation hubs, industrial complexes, city centers, and critical infrastructure requiring active surveillance. The DAHUA DH-ASA-1222E combines high-performance PTZ mechanics, intelligent tracking, and exceptional low-light imaging in a professional-grade solution for comprehensive area security.</p> </div>', NULL, NULL, 44, '2025-12-21 14:17:39', '2025-12-21 14:17:39', NULL),
(20, 'DAHUA DH-PFS3008-8ET-L-V2 PoE Network Switch', 'dahua-dh-pfs3008-8et-l-v2-poe-network-switch', 1400.00, 'products/c5TBh8iX43k2GOiXc8OiDRv1hYWeKPwzbhAdgYwx.webp', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">DAHUA DH-PFS3008-8ET-L-V2</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">8-Port PoE+ Switch for Surveillance Systems</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">An 8-port Gigabit PoE+ network switch designed specifically for IP surveillance systems, featuring 802.3at PoE+ support, VLAN capability, and robust construction. Perfect for powering and connecting multiple IP cameras in security installations.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">DAHUA DH-PFS3008-8ET-L-V2 8-Port PoE Network Switch</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Professional Surveillance-Grade PoE+ Power</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">This 8-port Gigabit switch provides IEEE 802.3at PoE+ (Power over Ethernet Plus) support on all eight ports, delivering up to 30 watts per port with a total power budget of 125 watts. Designed specifically for surveillance applications, it reliably powers high-performance IP cameras, PTZ units, and other PoE devices while simplifying installation by eliminating the need for separate power cables and outlets near each camera location.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">High-Speed Gigabit Connectivity</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring eight 10/100/1000BASE-T Ethernet ports with auto-negotiation and auto-MDI/MDIX, the switch ensures optimal data transfer speeds for high-resolution video streams. The non-blocking switching architecture provides wire-speed performance across all ports simultaneously, preventing network bottlenecks when multiple cameras are streaming high-bitrate 4K or 5MP video footage concurrently.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Advanced Network Management Features</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The switch supports essential network management capabilities including VLAN (Virtual LAN) configuration for segregating camera traffic from other network data, QoS (Quality of Service) prioritization to ensure smooth video streaming, and port-based bandwidth control. These features optimize network performance for surveillance systems, reducing latency and packet loss that could affect video quality.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Robust Construction and Reliability</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Built with surveillance-grade components and featuring a sturdy metal housing, the switch is designed for continuous 24/7 operation in demanding environments. It includes enhanced surge protection on all Ethernet ports to safeguard connected cameras from voltage spikes and electrical interference, a critical feature for outdoor surveillance installations exposed to weather-related electrical disturbances.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Surveillance-Specific Optimizations</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Specifically engineered for video surveillance networks, the switch includes features like large packet support (up to 9216 bytes) to handle jumbo frames from high-resolution cameras, IGMP snooping for efficient multicast video streaming to multiple NVRs or monitoring stations, and broadcast storm control to prevent network congestion from faulty devices.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Power Management and Protection</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The switch incorporates intelligent power management with per-port PoE control, allowing administrators to enable/disable PoE power to individual ports remotely or on a schedule. It includes comprehensive protection against short circuits, overloads, and over-temperature conditions, automatically resetting ports when faults are detected to maintain system uptime.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Flexible Deployment Options</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">With multiple installation options including desktop placement, wall mounting (using included brackets), or rack mounting (with optional rack ears), the switch adapts to various surveillance deployment scenarios. Its compact design and quiet, fanless operation make it suitable for installation in equipment closets, control rooms, or even environmental enclosures near camera clusters.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Ideal for small to medium surveillance systems, retail security installations, office building camera networks, and educational campus security deployments. The DAHUA DH-PFS3008-8ET-L-V2 provides reliable, surveillance-optimized network infrastructure that simplifies installation while ensuring stable power and data delivery to IP cameras and security devices.</p> </div>\n', NULL, NULL, 13, '2025-12-21 14:23:50', '2025-12-21 14:23:50', NULL);
