(21, 'ZKTeco F18 Biometric Fingerprint Access Control', 'zkteco-f18-biometric-fingerprint-access-control', 15000.00, 'products/llMqxXpaE0YHgzCr9YKBnYiABk6ejd2Yk4rRo651.webp', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">ZKTeco F18</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Standalone Fingerprint Access Control Terminal</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A compact standalone fingerprint access control device featuring 3,000 fingerprint capacity, 3,000 event logs, and support for PIN and RFID cards. Designed for secure entry control in offices, small businesses, and restricted areas.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">ZKTeco F18 Biometric Fingerprint Access Control Terminal</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">High-Performance Fingerprint Recognition</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The F18 features advanced optical fingerprint sensor technology with ZKTeco\'s proprietary algorithm for fast and accurate biometric identification. With a false acceptance rate (FAR) of less than 0.0001% and false rejection rate (FRR) of less than 0.01%, it delivers reliable security performance. The device supports 1:1 verification and 1:N identification modes, processing fingerprints in under 1 second for efficient access management.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Multi-Mode Authentication Options</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">In addition to fingerprint recognition, the F18 supports multiple authentication methods including PIN codes (4-8 digits) and 125kHz EM RFID card reading. The device allows for flexible verification combinations such as fingerprint only, card only, PIN only, fingerprint+PIN, or card+PIN, providing adaptable security levels for different access requirements and user preferences.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Substantial User Capacity</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">With capacity for 3,000 fingerprint templates, 3,000 RFID cards, and 3,000 PIN codes, the terminal accommodates medium-sized organizations or multi-tenant buildings. The device stores 3,000 event logs with detailed information including user ID, verification method, date, and time, which can be reviewed directly on the device or downloaded via management software.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Standalone Operation with Flexible Connectivity</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Operating as a fully standalone device, the F18 functions without requiring constant connection to a computer. It features USB 2.0 interface for data transfer and configuration, as well as TCP/IP network connectivity (via optional network module) for centralized management across multiple devices. The terminal supports Weigand output (26/34 bit) for integration with third-party access control systems.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Robust Hardware Construction</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Housed in a durable zinc alloy casing with IP65-rated weatherproof protection, the F18 withstands harsh environmental conditions including dust, rain, and temperature extremes. The vandal-resistant design features tamper detection with alarm output, while the high-resolution LCD screen provides clear user prompts and administrative menus even in bright lighting conditions.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Advanced Security and Management Features</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The terminal includes anti-passback functionality, duress alarm support, holiday scheduling, and time zone management for complex access scenarios. Administrators can define multiple user groups with different access privileges and create up to 100 time schedules with 16 time segments each, enabling precise control over when and where users can gain entry.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Easy Installation and Configuration</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Designed for straightforward installation, the F18 includes a built-in door strike relay (12V DC/2A) and exit button input, supporting typical single-door access control configurations. The intuitive ZKBioSecurity management software allows administrators to easily enroll users, configure settings, generate reports, and monitor access events from a central computer.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Ideal for office buildings, server rooms, laboratories, storage facilities, small to medium enterprises, and any environment requiring reliable biometric access control. The ZKTeco F18 combines robust fingerprint technology, flexible authentication options, and standalone operation in a cost-effective package suitable for various security applications.</p> </div>', NULL, NULL, 31, '2025-12-21 14:28:59', '2025-12-21 14:28:59', NULL),
(22, 'HP USB-C to RJ45 Adapter (V7W66AA)', 'hp-usb-c-to-rj45-adapter-v7w66aa', 3900.00, 'products/0lUtwwyUzH7rmSppWz04KMK39tFp58Fe2NblGIu9.webp', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">HP USB-C to RJ45 Adapter (V7W66AA)</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Gigabit Ethernet Adapter for Modern Laptops</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A compact USB-C to Gigabit Ethernet adapter providing reliable wired network connectivity for modern laptops and tablets. Featuring plug-and-play operation, it delivers stable Gigabit speeds for business, travel, and professional use where Wi-Fi is unreliable or unavailable.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">HP USB-C to RJ45 Adapter (V7W66AA)</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">High-Speed Gigabit Ethernet Connectivity</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">This adapter provides full Gigabit Ethernet performance (10/100/1000 Mbps) through a single USB-C port, delivering reliable wired network connectivity that outperforms most wireless connections. Utilizing a Realtek RTL8153 chipset, it ensures stable data transfer rates ideal for bandwidth-intensive tasks such as large file transfers, video conferencing, VoIP calls, and remote desktop sessions where connection stability is critical.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Universal USB-C Compatibility</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Designed for modern computing devices, the adapter works seamlessly with HP and non-HP laptops, tablets, and 2-in-1 devices featuring USB-C ports. It supports USB 3.1 Gen 1 (5 Gbps) standards and is backward compatible with USB 3.0 and USB 2.0 systems. The plug-and-play design requires no additional drivers for most operating systems, including Windows 10/11, macOS, Chrome OS, and Linux distributions with kernel version 3.0 or later.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Compact and Portable Design</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring a sleek, pocket-sized aluminum housing, the adapter is built for portability and daily use. Measuring just 6.5 cm in length and weighing only 25 grams, it easily fits in laptop bags, backpacks, or even pockets. The integrated 15 cm USB-C cable provides flexibility for various laptop orientations while maintaining a clean, professional appearance on desktops and workspaces.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Advanced Network Features</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Beyond basic connectivity, the adapter supports Wake-on-LAN (WoL) functionality for remote computer activation, enabling IT administrators to manage devices across networks. It features Auto MDI/MDIX crossover detection, eliminating the need for crossover cables when connecting directly to other network devices. The integrated LED indicators provide at-a-glance status information for both link activity and network speed.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Reliable Performance and Power Efficiency</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Engineered for business-grade reliability, the adapter operates within a wide temperature range (0C to 40C / 32F to 104F) and features ESD protection to safeguard connected devices from electrostatic discharge. With low power consumption (typically under 1.5W) and support for USB bus power, it functions without requiring external power sources, making it ideal for mobile professionals and travelers.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Enterprise and Professional Applications</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The adapter is particularly valuable in corporate environments where secure, stable connections are essential for accessing sensitive data, connecting to corporate VPNs, or participating in video conferences. It\'s also ideal for hotel rooms with wired internet only, conference centers, industrial settings with Wi-Fi interference, and any location where wireless signals are weak, congested, or insecure.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Warranty and Support</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Backed by HP\'s standard 1-year limited warranty, this adapter is tested for compatibility with HP business and consumer devices. It comes with HP\'s reliable customer support and is part of HP\'s ecosystem of business accessories designed to complement their computing devices while maintaining cross-platform compatibility.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Perfect for business travelers, remote workers, IT professionals, students, and anyone needing reliable wired connectivity for modern USB-C laptops. Whether used in hotel rooms, office environments, conference centers, or home offices, the HP USB-C to RJ45 Adapter provides dependable Gigabit Ethernet performance in a compact, portable form factor that complements today\'s slim-profile computing devices.</p> </div>', NULL, NULL, 1, '2025-12-21 14:34:19', '2025-12-21 14:34:19', NULL),
(23, 'Samsung Watch Wireless Charger', 'samsung-watch-wireless-charger', 4000.00, 'products/OnKs3mQ6fJMaI9VQqr5BM4braKQxovn8yz0Q44n8.jpg', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Samsung Watch Wireless Charger</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Magnetic Wireless Charging Pad for Galaxy Watches</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A dedicated wireless charging pad with magnetic alignment for Samsung Galaxy Watch series. Featuring compact design and reliable Qi-based charging, it provides convenient overnight or desktop charging for your smartwatch without cables.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">Samsung Watch Wireless Charger</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Magnetic Alignment Technology</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">This wireless charger utilizes Samsung\'s proprietary magnetic alignment system that automatically snaps your Galaxy Watch into the perfect charging position. The built-in magnets ensure precise contact between the charger and watch charging coils, optimizing charging efficiency and preventing misalignment that can interrupt charging cycles. The secure magnetic hold keeps the watch in place even if the charging pad is bumped or moved slightly.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Qi Wireless Charging Standard</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Compliant with the universal Qi wireless charging standard, the charger delivers up to 5W of power for efficient charging of compatible Samsung Galaxy Watch models including the Galaxy Watch 4, Watch 5, Watch 6, and earlier compatible versions. The Qi-certified technology ensures safe, regulated power delivery with built-in protection against over-voltage, over-current, and overheating during charging sessions.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Compact and Portable Design</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring a slim, circular profile with a soft-touch silicone surface, the charger measures just 60mm in diameter and 15mm in height, making it highly portable for travel or desk use. The lightweight construction (approximately 50g) and included 1.5-meter USB-C to USB-A cable provide flexibility for placement beside your bed, on your office desk, or in your travel bag for on-the-go charging.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">LED Charging Indicator</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">A discreet LED indicator on the front of the charger provides clear visual feedback: solid blue light indicates successful connection and active charging, while flashing blue light signals improper alignment or charging issues. The low-intensity LED is designed to be visible but not disruptive in dark bedroom environments during overnight charging.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Versatile Charging Applications</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Beyond overnight bedside charging, the pad\'s compact design makes it ideal for desktop use in office settings, allowing you to conveniently charge your watch while working. The non-slip silicone surface prevents sliding on smooth surfaces, and the charger maintains optimal performance whether placed horizontally on a table or mounted vertically using optional adhesive mounts (not included).</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Device Compatibility</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Officially compatible with Samsung Galaxy Watch 4 (40mm, 44mm), Galaxy Watch 5 (40mm, 44mm, 45mm), Galaxy Watch 6 (40mm, 44mm), and Galaxy Watch Active 2. Also compatible with other Qi-enabled devices including Samsung Galaxy Buds series (when placed correctly) and other Qi-compatible smartwatches, though magnetic alignment may not function with non-Samsung devices.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Travel-Friendly Features</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">With universal 100-240V input voltage compatibility through its USB power adapter (sold separately or using your existing 5V/2A adapter), the charger works worldwide. The compact size fits easily in luggage, and the magnetic hold prevents the watch from dislodging during transport when placed in bags or cases.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Perfect for Samsung Galaxy Watch owners seeking a convenient, cable-free charging solution for bedside tables, office desks, or travel. Whether used as a primary charger at home or a secondary charger at work, this wireless charging pad provides reliable, efficient power delivery with the convenience of magnetic alignment that ensures your watch is always properly positioned for optimal charging.</p> </div>', NULL, NULL, 96, '2025-12-21 14:39:09', '2025-12-21 14:39:09', NULL),
(24, 'Magnizon 3-Phase UPS MU30KXL  30kVA True Online Double Conversion UPS with Unity Power Factor', 'magnizon-3-phase-ups-mu30kxl-30kva-true-online-double-conversion-ups-with-unity-power-factor', 920000.00, 'products/81Rhfe2yZSt9hUMFWMo8G40ikBHcWQI38f21ag17.jpg', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Magnizon MU30KXL</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">30kVA Three-Phase True Online Double Conversion UPS</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A high-capacity three-phase UPS delivering pure sine wave output with unity power factor (1.0) for critical infrastructure. Featuring online double conversion technology, advanced battery management, and scalable runtime, it ensures uninterrupted power for data centers, industrial equipment, and enterprise systems.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">Magnizon 3-Phase UPS MU30KXL  30kVA True Online Double Conversion UPS with Unity Power Factor</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">True Online Double Conversion Technology</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The MU30KXL employs true online double conversion technology, continuously converting AC input to DC and then back to clean, stable AC output. This provides complete isolation from all utility power problems including voltage fluctuations, frequency variations, harmonics, and complete blackouts. With zero transfer time to battery, connected equipment experiences no interruption even during complete power failures, making it ideal for mission-critical applications.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Unity Power Factor (1.0 PF) Capability</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring a unity power factor of 1.0, this UPS delivers maximum usable power (30kVA equals 30kW) without reactive power losses, making it significantly more efficient than traditional UPS systems with 0.8 or 0.9 power factors. This allows the full 30kVA capacity to be utilized for active power, supporting more equipment on the same kVA rating and reducing overall system costs.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Three-Phase Input and Output</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Designed for industrial and commercial applications, the UPS accepts three-phase AC input (380/400/415V, 50/60Hz) and delivers three-phase output with precise voltage regulation (1%). The system automatically synchronizes with generator power during extended outages and features adjustable input voltage windows to accommodate varying utility conditions while minimizing battery usage.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Advanced Battery Management System</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Incorporating intelligent battery management with temperature compensation, automatic battery testing, and predictive failure analysis. The system supports external battery packs for extended runtime, with smart charging algorithms that optimize battery life through float and equalization charging cycles. Battery status is continuously monitored with precise runtime calculations based on actual load.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">High Efficiency Operation</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Achieving up to 96% efficiency in online mode through advanced IGBT technology and high-frequency switching design. The Eco mode option increases efficiency to 99% while maintaining voltage regulation. The intelligent fan control system adjusts cooling based on load and temperature, reducing energy consumption and extending component life.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Comprehensive Monitoring and Management</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring a large LCD display with multilingual interface showing input/output parameters, battery status, and system diagnostics. Includes multiple communication ports (RS232, USB, SNMP, dry contacts) for integration with network management systems. Optional network cards enable remote monitoring, configuration, and shutdown commands via web browser or network management software.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Robust Protection Features</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Provides complete protection against power anomalies including surges, spikes, sags, brownouts, and electrical noise. The pure sine wave output ensures compatibility with sensitive electronic equipment including servers, medical devices, and industrial control systems. Built-in bypass switch enables maintenance without power interruption, while automatic overload protection safeguards the UPS and connected equipment.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Scalable and Redundant Configurations</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Supports parallel operation for N+1 redundancy or capacity expansion up to 6 units (180kVA). Hot-swappable power modules and batteries enable maintenance without system shutdown. The modular design allows for future capacity upgrades as power requirements grow, protecting long-term investment.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Ideal for data centers, hospital medical equipment, industrial manufacturing systems, telecommunications infrastructure, financial trading floors, and any application requiring clean, uninterrupted three-phase power. The Magnizon MU30KXL combines enterprise-grade reliability, high efficiency, and advanced management features in a robust UPS solution for critical power protection.</p> </div>', NULL, NULL, 51, '2025-12-21 14:44:49', '2025-12-21 14:44:49', NULL),
(25, 'Magnizon MU650VA 650VA Line Interactive UPS  360W Output for Reliable Power Protection', 'magnizon-mu650va-650va-line-interactive-ups-360w-output-for-reliable-power-protection', 8500.00, 'products/lZvCHVzJ85XEQXZP4IfHp8MSz1YK2NoJcuCcMMRa.webp', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Magnizon MU650VA</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">650VA/360W Line Interactive UPS for Home & Office</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A compact line-interactive UPS providing battery backup and surge protection for desktop computers, networking equipment, and essential electronics. With 6 outlets (3 battery-backed), AVR, and audible alarms, it safeguards against blackouts, brownouts, and power fluctuations.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">Magnizon MU650VA 650VA Line Interactive UPS  360W Output for Reliable Power Protection</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Line Interactive UPS Technology</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The MU650VA employs advanced line-interactive technology with automatic voltage regulation (AVR) to correct minor voltage fluctuations without switching to battery power. This extends battery life by reducing unnecessary discharge cycles while providing clean, stable power to connected equipment. The system responds within 4-6 milliseconds to switch to battery backup during complete power failures, ensuring uninterrupted operation for critical devices.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Optimized Power Capacity</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Rated at 650VA/360W, this UPS provides sufficient runtime for typical desktop computer systems, monitors, and networking equipment. Under half load (180W), it delivers approximately 10-15 minutes of backup time, allowing for safe system shutdown or continued operation during short outages. The pure sine wave output ensures compatibility with active PFC power supplies found in modern computers and sensitive electronics.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Comprehensive Outlet Protection</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring six NEMA 5-15R outlets  three battery backup and surge protected outlets, plus three surge-only protected outlets. This configuration allows users to prioritize critical equipment for battery backup while providing surge protection for additional peripherals. The surge protection rating of 650 Joules safeguards against voltage spikes, with EMI/RFI filtering to reduce electrical noise.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Intelligent Battery Management</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Equipped with a maintenance-free sealed lead-acid (SLA) battery with typical lifespan of 3-5 years under normal conditions. The UPS features automatic self-test every 14 days to verify battery health and charging circuit functionality. Cold-start capability allows the UPS to power connected devices even without utility power, useful during setup or maintenance.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">User-Friendly Interface and Alerts</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">A front-panel LCD display provides real-time information including input/output voltage, battery charge level, load percentage, and estimated runtime. Audible alarms alert users to different conditions: four distinct tones indicate utility power loss, low battery, overload, and fault conditions. Mute buttons allow temporary silencing of alarms during nighttime operation.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Automatic Voltage Regulation (AVR)</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The built-in AVR circuitry automatically boosts low voltage (as low as 160V) and reduces high voltage (up to 280V) without using battery power. This feature is particularly valuable in areas with unstable grid power, brownouts, or voltage sags, as it maintains proper voltage levels to connected equipment and prevents unnecessary battery drain.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Compact and Practical Design</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">With dimensions of 290 x 135 x 215 mm and weighing 6.8 kg, the UPS fits conveniently under desks, on shelves, or in home office setups. Cable management features include rear cord wrap and sufficient spacing between outlets to accommodate bulky power adapters. The black textured finish blends with most office and home electronics.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Data Line Protection</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Includes two RJ11 telephone/DSL ports and one RJ45 Ethernet port for surge protection of modem and network connections. This additional protection prevents power surges from entering through communication lines, safeguarding modems, routers, and network interfaces from damage caused by lightning-induced surges on telephone or cable lines.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Ideal for home offices, small businesses, point-of-sale systems, networking equipment, and desktop workstations. The Magnizon MU650VA provides essential power protection with sufficient runtime for graceful system shutdowns, protecting data integrity and hardware from unexpected power interruptions and electrical disturbances.</p> </div>\n', NULL, NULL, 51, '2025-12-21 14:55:32', '2025-12-21 14:55:32', NULL),
(26, 'Huawei PDU Rack Power Distribution (PDU2000-32-1PH-20/4-B9)', 'huawei-pdu-rack-power-distribution-pdu2000-32-1ph-204-b9', 26000.00, 'products/qn7FWq7oRkPPFGLMnA2BcEXu9R85qC46QrKrDF09.jpg', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Huawei PDU2000-32-1PH-20/4-B9</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">32-Outlet 1U Rack PDU with Metering & Remote Control</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A professional 1U rack-mount power distribution unit featuring 32 C13 outlets, input current monitoring, and IP-based remote power control. Designed for data center and server room applications requiring precise power management and individual outlet switching.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">Huawei PDU Rack Power Distribution (PDU2000-32-1PH-20/4-B9)</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">High-Density Power Distribution</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">This 1U rack-mount PDU provides 32 IEC C13 outlets in a space-efficient design, enabling maximum equipment density in standard 19-inch server racks. With a total power capacity of 16A/230V (3.68kW), it supports simultaneous power delivery to multiple servers, network switches, storage systems, and other rack-mounted equipment, eliminating the need for multiple power strips and reducing cable clutter.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Intelligent Power Monitoring</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring built-in current monitoring with 1% accuracy, the PDU provides real-time power consumption data for the entire unit. The front-panel LCD display shows key parameters including input voltage, current, power, power factor, and energy consumption (kWh). This enables precise capacity planning, load balancing across phases, and identification of underutilized or overloaded circuits.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Remote Power Management</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Each of the 32 outlets supports individual remote on/off control and reboot functionality via web interface, SNMP, or Telnet/SSH. This allows administrators to power cycle unresponsive equipment, implement scheduled power sequences, or remotely disconnect non-essential devices without physical access to the data center. Outlets can be grouped for coordinated control of multi-device systems.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Advanced Network Connectivity</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Equipped with dual 10/100 Mbps Ethernet ports supporting link aggregation and failover for network redundancy. The embedded web server provides intuitive management through a browser-based interface, while support for SNMP v1/v2c/v3 enables integration with enterprise network management systems like Huawei eSight, Nagios, or SolarWinds.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Comprehensive Safety Features</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Incorporates multiple protection mechanisms including overload protection with configurable thresholds (60%-100% of rated current), over-temperature protection with thermal sensors, and IP20 finger-safe outlet design. The robust metal housing provides electromagnetic shielding and includes multiple mounting options for horizontal, vertical, or zero-U mounting configurations.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Environmental Monitoring</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Optional external temperature/humidity sensor support enables environmental monitoring within the rack enclosure. The PDU can trigger alerts when temperature thresholds are exceeded, helping prevent equipment overheating and enabling proactive cooling management before thermal issues impact system reliability.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Enterprise-Grade Reliability</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Designed for 24/7 operation in data center environments with MTBF exceeding 150,000 hours. Features include dual power supplies with automatic failover, configurable alarm thresholds for voltage, current, and temperature, and event logging with syslog support for compliance and troubleshooting purposes.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Flexible Integration and Control</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Supports multiple user authentication levels (administrator, user, guest) with granular permission settings. Integration with data center infrastructure management (DCIM) systems enables coordinated control with cooling units and other environmental systems. The PDU supports firmware upgrades without service interruption and includes automated power-up sequencing to prevent inrush current issues.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Ideal for enterprise data centers, cloud service providers, colocation facilities, and server rooms requiring intelligent power distribution with remote management capabilities. The Huawei PDU2000-32-1PH-20/4-B9 combines high outlet density, precise monitoring, and granular control in a reliable solution that enhances operational efficiency and reduces data center management overhead.</p> </div>\n', NULL, NULL, 52, '2025-12-21 15:00:53', '2025-12-21 15:00:53', NULL),
(27, 'Eaton 16Amps Automatic Transfer Switch (EATS16N)', 'eaton-16amps-automatic-transfer-switch-eats16n', 152000.00, 'products/hyQCkllqHDewaEPB0xyG9T41WyoNAXPOWIbKgo91.jpg', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Eaton EATS16N</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">16A Automatic Transfer Switch for Generator Power</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A compact automatic transfer switch designed for seamless power transition between utility and generator sources. Rated at 16A/230V, it provides automatic failover during outages and protects against backfeeding for residential and small commercial backup power systems.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">Eaton 16A Automatic Transfer Switch (EATS16N)</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Seamless Automatic Power Transfer</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The EATS16N automatically detects utility power failures and transfers the connected load to an alternative power source (typically a standby generator) within 1-2 seconds, ensuring minimal interruption to critical circuits. When utility power is restored, it automatically retransfers back after a user-configurable delay (typically 1-5 minutes), allowing grid stabilization before reconnection and protecting sensitive equipment from power fluctuations.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Advanced Safety and Protection Features</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Engineered with comprehensive safety mechanisms including a mechanical interlock system that physically prevents both utility and generator power sources from being connected simultaneously. This critical feature eliminates the risk of backfeeding, which could endanger utility line workers during power restoration. The switch also incorporates surge protection and short-circuit protection to safeguard both the transfer switch and connected equipment.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Intelligent Load Management</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Rated for 16A continuous operation at 230V (3.68kW), the transfer switch can manage essential household or small business circuits. It includes priority circuit management capabilities, allowing users to designate critical loads (refrigeration, lighting, security systems) that receive power first during generator operation, ensuring optimal use of limited generator capacity during extended outages.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Generator Exercise Function</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Features an integrated weekly generator exercise timer that automatically starts the connected generator for a programmable duration (typically 10-30 minutes) to ensure readiness and maintain battery charge. This automated maintenance function extends generator life by preventing fuel system issues and ensuring reliable operation when actually needed during power outages.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">User-Friendly Operation and Monitoring</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Equipped with a clear status indicator panel showing power source status (utility or generator), transfer switch position, and any fault conditions. LED indicators provide immediate visual feedback, while optional remote status panels (sold separately) allow monitoring from inside the home. The compact design includes easy-to-access wiring terminals with clear markings for simplified installation.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Robust Construction and Compliance</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Constructed with industrial-grade components housed in a NEMA 3R-rated enclosure suitable for indoor or outdoor installation. The switch mechanism utilizes silver-plated contacts for reliable performance and long service life. Compliant with international electrical standards including IEC 60947-6-1 and carries CE marking for European market acceptance.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Flexible Installation Options</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Designed for straightforward installation with multiple mounting options including wall mounting, panel mounting, or integration into existing electrical distribution panels. The compact dimensions (approximately 300 x 200 x 150 mm) allow installation in limited spaces. Includes provisions for both hardwired and plug-in generator connections depending on local electrical code requirements.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Compatibility and Integration</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Compatible with most portable and stationary generators up to 16A output, as well as inverter generators. Can be integrated with Eaton\'s broader home energy management systems and works with conventional utility power sources. Includes dry contacts for external alarm signaling and remote start/stop functionality with compatible generator models.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Ideal for residential backup power systems, small offices, retail establishments, telecom cabinets, and agricultural applications requiring reliable automatic power source switching. The Eaton EATS16N provides professional-grade automatic transfer functionality in a compact, reliable package that ensures critical loads remain powered during utility outages while maintaining essential safety protections.</p> </div>\n', NULL, NULL, 52, '2025-12-21 15:05:02', '2025-12-21 15:05:02', NULL),
(28, 'Vention KSDH0 Articulating Desk Phone Stand with 360 Rotatable Base Gray Aluminium Alloy Type', 'vention-ksdh0-articulating-desk-phone-stand-with-360-rotatable-base-gray-aluminium-alloy-type', 1700.00, 'products/iaqzODbI2cHrTUsBtfM5xMwsLeh9um02c2Ws1MGR.webp', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Vention KSDH0</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Articulating Desk Phone Stand with 360 Rotatable Base</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A premium aluminum alloy phone stand featuring full-motion articulation and 360 rotation for optimal smartphone positioning. Designed for desks, workstations, and home offices, it provides secure holding and adjustable viewing angles for video calls, media consumption, and hands-free operation.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">Vention KSDH0 Articulating Desk Phone Stand with 360 Rotatable Base  Gray Aluminum Alloy Type</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Fully Articulated Movement System</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The KSDH0 features a sophisticated five-joint articulation system that enables virtually unlimited positioning possibilities. Each joint maintains tension-adjustable friction, allowing smooth movement and stable holding at any angle. The stand extends up to 40cm from its base, retracts to a compact 20cm, and provides 360 continuous rotation at both the base and phone holder, enabling perfect landscape or portrait orientation from any viewing position.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Universal Phone Compatibility</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Equipped with an adjustable spring-loaded phone clamp that accommodates devices from 4\" to 7\" in width (compatible with all smartphones up to the largest phablet sizes). The clamp features soft silicone pads that securely grip devices without scratching or damaging cases, while providing sufficient clearance for charging ports and buttons. The holder can be tilted 90 to achieve optimal viewing angles for video calls, reading, or media playback.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Premium Aluminum Alloy Construction</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Crafted from high-grade 6063 aluminum alloy with sandblasted and anodized gray finish, the stand combines lightweight durability with premium aesthetics. The metal construction provides exceptional stability, supporting devices up to 1kg without wobbling or sagging. All moving parts feature precision CNC machining with steel reinforcement at stress points for long-term reliability and smooth operation.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Versatile Desk Mounting Options</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The weighted circular base (15cm diameter) provides exceptional stability without requiring permanent mounting. The base features a non-slip silicone ring that prevents sliding on smooth surfaces while protecting desktop finishes. For permanent installations, the base includes four pre-drilled holes for optional screw mounting to desks, workbenches, or studio furniture.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Cable Management Integration</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Designed with integrated cable routing channels along the arm segments, allowing neat organization of charging cables. The phone holder includes a dedicated cable clip to secure charging cables in position, preventing disconnection during adjustment. This thoughtful design maintains clean desk aesthetics while ensuring continuous power during extended use.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Multi-Scenario Applications</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Perfect for video conferencing setups, transforming any smartphone into a professional webcam at optimal eye level. Equally suitable for recipe viewing in kitchens, sheet music display for musicians, document reference for students, or as a secondary display for notifications and monitoring apps. The stand enables comfortable viewing angles that reduce neck strain during extended use.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Professional and Home Office Use</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Ideal for remote workers, content creators, streamers, and professionals who frequently use smartphones for video calls or as secondary displays. The neutral gray aluminum finish complements modern office decor, while the precise adjustability supports ergonomic workstation setups that comply with occupational health recommendations for screen positioning.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Perfect for home offices, corporate workstations, studio setups, retail counters, or kitchen installations where flexible smartphone positioning enhances productivity and convenience. The Vention KSDH0 combines professional-grade articulation, premium construction, and versatile functionality in a desk accessory that transforms smartphone usage from handheld to hands-free with optimal ergonomics.</p> </div>\n', NULL, NULL, 96, '2025-12-21 15:07:35', '2025-12-21 15:07:35', NULL),
(29, 'Vention 3-Port USB (C + A + A) Universal Travel Adapter (20W/18W/18W) Black, FJEB0', 'vention-3-port-usb-c-a-a-universal-travel-adapter-20w18w18w-black-fjeb0', 2800.00, 'products/6WMe69ypRywlfNlbpSSFS5G2ATiu5xCBPvEWUiOc.webp', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Vention FJEB0</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">3-Port Universal Travel Adapter with 56W Total Power</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A compact international travel adapter featuring USB-C (20W) and dual USB-A (18W each) ports for simultaneous charging of multiple devices. With foldable pins and worldwide plug compatibility, it\'s designed for travelers needing versatile charging solutions across different countries.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">Vention 3-Port USB (C + A + A) Universal Travel Adapter (20W/18W/18W) Black, FJEB0</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Global Travel Compatibility</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring four interchangeable plug adapters (US/EU/UK/AU) that seamlessly integrate into the compact main body, this travel adapter supports electrical outlets in over 200 countries worldwide. Each adapter piece stores securely within the housing when not in use, and the entire unit folds down to just 65mm  60mm  30mm for maximum portability in luggage or carry-on bags.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Intelligent Multi-Port Charging</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Equipped with three high-speed charging ports: one USB-C port delivering up to 20W Power Delivery (PD 3.0) for fast-charging modern smartphones and tablets, plus two USB-A ports each providing up to 18W with Quick Charge 3.0 technology. The smart power allocation system distributes up to 56W total output, automatically optimizing current based on connected devices\' requirements when multiple ports are used simultaneously.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Advanced Safety Protection</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Incorporates comprehensive protection circuitry including over-current protection (OCP), over-voltage protection (OVP), short-circuit protection (SCP), over-temperature protection (OTP), and resetable fuse protection. The adapter meets international safety standards including CE, FCC, and RoHS certifications, with built-in surge protection up to 600V to safeguard connected electronics from voltage spikes in unstable power grids.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Universal Voltage Compatibility</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Supports wide input voltage range of 100-240V AC at 50/60Hz, automatically adapting to electrical systems worldwide without manual switching. This dual-voltage capability ensures safe operation whether connected to 110V systems in North America or 220-240V systems in Europe, Asia, and other regions, making it truly universal for international travel.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Fast Charging Protocols Support</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The USB-C port supports Power Delivery 3.0 with programmable power supply (PPS) for Samsung Super Fast Charging, while USB-A ports support Quick Charge 3.0, Huawei FCP, Samsung AFC, and standard 5V/2.4A charging. This comprehensive protocol compatibility ensures optimal charging speeds for devices from Apple, Samsung, Huawei, Google, and other major manufacturers.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Compact and Durable Design</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Constructed from fire-resistant PC+ABS material with matte black finish that resists scratches and fingerprints. The folding plug mechanism features reinforced hinges tested to withstand over 10,000 insertion/removal cycles. Weighing only 150g, the compact design minimizes luggage space while the rounded edges prevent snagging on clothing or bag interiors.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Travel-Specific Features</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Includes an LED power indicator that provides visual confirmation of proper electrical connection. The plug adapters feature secure locking mechanisms that prevent accidental detachment during use. The overall design accommodates grounded and ungrounded outlets, with sufficient clearance around the adapter body to prevent blocking adjacent outlets in crowded power strips.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Energy Efficient Operation</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Utilizes high-efficiency switching technology with conversion efficiency up to 90%, minimizing energy waste during charging. The adapter enters low-power standby mode when devices are fully charged, with standby power consumption below 0.075W to comply with international energy efficiency regulations and reduce unnecessary power drain.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Ideal for frequent travelers, business professionals, tourists, digital nomads, and families needing reliable multi-device charging across different countries. The Vention FJEB0 combines global plug compatibility, high-speed charging technology, and comprehensive safety features in a single compact unit that replaces multiple chargers and adapters, simplifying travel electronics while ensuring devices remain powered anywhere in the world.</p> </div>\n', NULL, NULL, 96, '2025-12-21 15:10:10', '2025-12-21 15:10:10', NULL);
