(30, 'Fanvil V62G Prime Business PoE IP Phone', 'fanvil-v62g-prime-business-poe-ip-phone', 8500.00, 'products/5csEC82SDkF6ePMJuYbnEfC2IvoEzm434X2Z3yx0.png', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Fanvil V62G Prime</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Premium Business IP Phone with 6-Line LCD & PoE</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A professional-grade IP phone featuring a 2.4\" color LCD, 6 SIP lines, HD voice, and Power over Ethernet support. Designed for executive offices and busy professionals requiring advanced telephony features, unified communications integration, and exceptional audio quality.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">Fanvil V62G Prime Business PoE IP Phone</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">High-Definition Voice Quality</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The V62G Prime delivers exceptional audio performance with wideband HD voice (G.722 codec) and Opus support for crystal-clear conversations. Featuring advanced acoustic technology including dual-microphone array with 120 pickup pattern and noise cancellation, it ensures optimal voice transmission even in noisy office environments. The high-quality speakerphone provides full-duplex audio without echo or clipping, making conference calls natural and productive.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Large 2.4\" Color LCD Display</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Centered around a vibrant 2.4-inch 320x240 pixel color TFT LCD with adjustable backlight brightness and viewing angle. The intuitive graphical interface displays six SIP lines simultaneously with presence indicators, call status, contact photos, and softkey functions. The display supports multiple languages and provides visual voicemail indicators, call history with details, and XML browser capabilities for custom applications.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Comprehensive SIP Protocol Support</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Supporting up to 6 SIP accounts/identities with independent registration status and configuration. Compatible with major IP PBX platforms including Asterisk, FreePBX, 3CX, Grandstream UCM, and Yeastar systems. The phone includes advanced telephony features such as call waiting, call transfer (attended/blind), call park, call pickup, intercom, auto-answer, and music on hold with customizable tones.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Power over Ethernet (PoE) Capability</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Fully compliant with IEEE 802.3af Power over Ethernet Class 2, allowing single-cable installation for both data and power. Includes a built-in PoE passthrough port on the secondary Ethernet interface, enabling daisy-chaining of another PoE device such as a wireless access point or secondary phone without requiring additional power injectors or outlets.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Dual Ethernet Ports with Gigabit Speed</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Equipped with two auto-sensing 10/100/1000 Mbps Ethernet ports with built-in switch functionality. The primary port connects to the network, while the secondary port allows connection of a computer, creating a convenient desktop pass-through that reduces cable clutter. Both ports support VLAN tagging (802.1Q/VLAN) for network segmentation and QoS prioritization.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Advanced Business Features</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Includes 5-way audio conferencing without external server requirements, Bluetooth 4.2 support for wireless headsets, and integrated EHS (Electronic Hook Switch) compatibility with popular headset brands. The phone supports LDAP directory integration for corporate contact lookup, XML push services for weather, stock, or custom information display, and programmable keys for speed dials, BLF (Busy Lamp Field) monitoring, and feature access.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Enterprise Security and Management</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Incorporates multiple security layers including TLS/SRTP encryption for secure signaling and media, 802.1X network authentication, and administrator password protection. Supports centralized provisioning via TR-069, HTTP/HTTPS, or TFTP with bulk configuration capabilities. The phone includes a built-in firewall with access control lists and DoS attack prevention.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Ergonomic Design and Build Quality</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Constructed with premium materials including a weighted base for stability and a user-friendly key layout with backlit buttons. The handset features noise-canceling technology and comfortable ergonomics, while the adjustable display stand allows optimal viewing angles. The phone meets rigorous business durability standards with MTBF exceeding 100,000 hours.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Ideal for executive offices, reception areas, contact centers, and professional workspaces requiring premium communication capabilities. The Fanvil V62G Prime combines sophisticated design, advanced telephony features, and superior audio quality in a business IP phone that enhances productivity while integrating seamlessly with modern unified communications ecosystems.</p> </div>', NULL, NULL, 60, '2025-12-22 01:47:45', '2025-12-22 01:47:45', NULL),
(31, 'Fanvil X7C Enterprise IP Phone', 'fanvil-x7c-enterprise-ip-phone', 18500.00, 'products/JIpfjlQ0JkB8S1mhp4rIapq5caO12rzxhSkOzo6W.png', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Fanvil X7C</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">7-inch Touchscreen Enterprise IP Phone</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A premium 7-inch capacitive touchscreen IP phone designed for modern enterprises, featuring Android OS, quad-core processor, and unified communications capabilities. With PoE support and extensive integration options, it serves as a complete desktop communications hub for professional environments.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">Fanvil X7C Enterprise IP Phone</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">7-inch High-Definition Touchscreen Display</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The X7C features a vibrant 7-inch capacitive touchscreen with 1024600 resolution, providing an intuitive Android-like interface for seamless navigation. The IPS panel delivers wide viewing angles and excellent visibility even in brightly lit office environments. The responsive touch interface supports multi-touch gestures, making it easy to access contacts, call history, applications, and phone settings with familiar smartphone-like interactions.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Android-Based Smart Platform</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Powered by Android 9.0 operating system with a quad-core 1.5GHz processor and 2GB RAM, the X7C functions as both a traditional IP phone and a smart communications terminal. The open Android platform allows installation of business applications from the Google Play Store, including Microsoft Teams, Zoom, CRM systems, productivity tools, and custom enterprise applications, transforming the phone into a complete desktop workstation.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Advanced Unified Communications</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Supporting up to 16 SIP accounts with simultaneous registration, the phone integrates voice, video, instant messaging, and presence information in a unified interface. Native integration with popular UC platforms including Microsoft Teams (Direct Routing), Zoom Phone, and Webex Calling provides seamless collaboration capabilities. The built-in 5MP front-facing camera enables video calls directly from the desktop phone.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">High-Fidelity Audio Technology</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Equipped with premium acoustic components including wideband HD audio with Opus codec support, dual omni-directional microphones with advanced noise cancellation, and a high-quality speaker system. The acoustic echo cancellation (AEC) and automatic gain control (AGC) ensure crystal-clear conversations whether using the handset, speakerphone, or Bluetooth headset.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Power over Ethernet and Connectivity</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Fully compliant with IEEE 802.3af/at PoE standards for single-cable installation. Features dual Gigabit Ethernet ports (10/100/1000 Mbps) with integrated switch functionality and PoE passthrough capability. Additional connectivity includes Bluetooth 5.0 for wireless headsets, dual-band Wi-Fi (802.11 a/b/g/n/ac), USB 2.0 port for peripherals, and microSD card slot for local storage expansion.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Enterprise-Grade Security</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Incorporates comprehensive security measures including hardware encryption engine, secure boot with digital signature verification, TLS 1.2/1.3 for SIP signaling, and SRTP for media encryption. Supports 802.1X network authentication, VPN (OpenVPN, L2TP, PPTP), and regular security updates through Fanvil\'s firmware management system. Administrative controls include remote management, configuration backup/restore, and detailed access logs.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Professional Business Features</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Includes advanced telephony functions such as multi-party conference calling (up to 8 participants), call recording (local or network), XML directory integration with LDAP/Active Directory, and customizable XML applications. The programmable physical keys (12 dual-color LEDs) provide quick access to speed dials, BLF monitoring, call features, and application shortcuts.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Flexible Deployment and Management</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Supports zero-touch provisioning via TR-069, HTTP/HTTPS, or TFTP for large-scale deployments. Compatible with major IP PBX platforms including 3CX, Asterisk, FreePBX, and Yeastar. The device management portal allows centralized configuration, firmware updates, and monitoring of all X7C phones across the enterprise with bulk operation capabilities.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Ideal for executive desks, conference rooms, reception areas, contact centers, and modern offices embracing digital transformation. The Fanvil X7C redefines the desktop phone by combining traditional telephony reliability with smart device functionality, creating a future-proof communications hub that enhances productivity and collaboration in the evolving workplace.</p> </div>', NULL, NULL, 60, '2025-12-22 01:52:05', '2025-12-22 01:52:05', NULL),
(32, 'Magnizon HG6048SW-LCD 6KVA/4.8KW Pure Sinewave Inverter with 40A Built-in Battery Charger | Reliable Power Solution for Homes & Businesses', 'magnizon-hg6048sw-lcd-6kva48kw-pure-sinewave-inverter-with-40a-built-in-battery-charger-reliable-power-solution-for-homes-businesses', 102000.00, 'products/fOfMAiZSvnS91PMhJkUabIQQPTGlFmLcg2rf3JDJ.webp', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Magnizon HG6048SW-LCD</h3> <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">6KVA/4.8KW Pure Sinewave Inverter-Charger</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600\">A powerful pure sine wave inverter with integrated 40A battery charger and LCD display. Providing 6000VA/4800W continuous power, it delivers clean AC output for sensitive electronics, appliances, and business equipment during outages or off-grid operation.</p> </div>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"> <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4\">Magnizon HG6048SW-LCD 6KVA/4.8KW Pure Sinewave Inverter with 40A Built-in Battery Charger | Reliable Power Solution for Homes & Businesses</h3><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Pure Sine Wave Output Technology</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">The HG6048SW-LCD generates a clean, stable pure sine wave output identical to utility grid power, ensuring compatibility with sensitive electronics including computers, medical equipment, variable-speed motors, and appliances with active power factor correction. With less than 3% total harmonic distortion (THD), it protects equipment from waveform-related damage and ensures optimal performance of inductive loads like refrigerators, air conditioners, and pumps.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">High-Capacity Power Output</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Rated at 6000VA/4800W continuous power with 12000VA surge capacity for 5 seconds, this inverter can power essential household circuits or small business equipment during outages. The unit supports 220-240VAC output at 50/60Hz and efficiently handles simultaneous operation of multiple appliances including refrigerators, lighting, fans, computers, and entertainment systems without overload conditions.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Intelligent 40A Battery Charger</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Incorporating a 3-stage smart charging system (bulk, absorption, float) with temperature compensation for optimal battery health and longevity. The 40A charger rapidly recharges battery banks when utility or generator power is available, with configurable charging parameters for different battery types (flooded, AGM, gel, lithium). Charging efficiency exceeds 90%, minimizing energy loss during recharge cycles.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Comprehensive LCD Monitoring System</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Featuring a backlit LCD display providing real-time monitoring of input/output voltage, battery voltage, charging current, load percentage, and operating mode. The interface includes visual alerts for fault conditions, battery status indicators, and programmable parameters. Multiple language support and intuitive menus simplify configuration for both residential and commercial users.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Multiple Operation Modes</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Supports versatile operation configurations including UPS mode (0ms transfer time for critical loads), line mode (utility power passthrough with battery charging), and energy saving mode (efficient operation with extended battery life). The automatic transfer switch seamlessly transitions between utility and inverter power within 10 milliseconds, ensuring uninterrupted operation of connected equipment.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Advanced Battery Management</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Compatible with 48V DC battery systems (42-60V range) and includes configurable low battery cut-off to prevent deep discharge damage. Features automatic equalization charging for flooded lead-acid batteries and programmable charging voltages for customized battery bank optimization. The system includes remote battery temperature sensor support for precise temperature compensation.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Robust Protection Features</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Incorporates comprehensive protection mechanisms: overload protection, short circuit protection, over-temperature protection, reverse polarity protection, and output over-voltage protection. The unit includes both audible and visual alarms for fault conditions and automatically enters protective shutdown when parameters exceed safe operating limits.</p><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3\">Flexible Installation Options</h4> <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Designed for wall mounting or floor installation with ventilation considerations. Includes multiple communication ports (USB, RS232) for remote monitoring and PC software integration. Parallel operation capability allows connection of up to 6 units for increased capacity or redundancy. The unit operates with high efficiency (up to 93%) and includes eco-mode for reduced no-load power consumption.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 italic\">Ideal for home backup power systems, small business continuity, off-grid cabins, telecom installations, retail stores, and workshops requiring reliable AC power from battery banks. The Magnizon HG6048SW-LCD combines substantial power capacity, intelligent battery management, and pure sine wave output in a comprehensive inverter-charger solution that bridges utility power interruptions while protecting sensitive equipment.</p> </div>', NULL, NULL, 62, '2025-12-22 02:10:00', '2025-12-22 02:10:00', NULL);

